        <updateDate>2022-09-28T15:08:42Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Protecting Domestic Violence and Stalking Victims Act of 2021</strong></p> <p>This bill extends federal firearms-related restrictions to individuals who are convicted of misdemeanor stalking offenses. The bill also broadens the scope of domestic violence offenses and court orders that trigger federal firearms-related restrictions. </p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
